<style>
  body, h1, h2, h3, p, a, button {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
  }

  body {
      background-color: #0a192f;
      color: #ccd6f6;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 20px;
  }

  .container {
      max-width: calc(100% - 400px);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #112240;
      border: 2px solid #64ffda;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #64ffda;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
  }

  p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  strong {
      color: #64ffda;
  }

  .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #0a192f;
      background-color: #64ffda;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
      background-color: #52d1b2;
  }

  .buttons {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
      .container {
          max-width: calc(100% - 200px);
      }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .container {
          max-width: calc(100% - 100px);
      }
      h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
      }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
          max-width: calc(100% - 40px);
          padding: 15px;
      }
      h1 {
          font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      p {
          font-size: 1rem;
      }
  }
</style>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>SensoCraft - Tech Carvaan 2025</h1>
    <h2>Organized by Government College of Engineering, Jalgaon</h2>
    
    <div class="details">
        <p><strong>📅 Event Date:</strong> 24th - 25th March 2025</p>
        <p><strong>📍 Venue:</strong> GCOEJ, Jalgaon</p>
        
        <h3>About the Event</h3>
        <p>SensoCraft is GCOEJ’s premier Tech Carvaan event, designed to foster innovation, collaboration, and creativity among tech enthusiasts. It provides a national platform for students, developers, and innovators to showcase their technical skills.</p>

        <h3>Event Highlights</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>✅ Cutting-edge challenges in technology</li>
            <li>✅ Real-world problem-solving opportunities</li>
            <li>✅ A collaborative and innovative learning environment</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Competition Themes</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>🔹 <strong>SensoCraft: Sensors & Instrumentation</strong> – Advancements in sensor technology and industrial automation</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>IoT & Automation</strong> – Smart technology solutions for real-world applications</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>AI & Machine Learning</strong> – AI-driven problem-solving and predictive analytics</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Smart Farming & Agri-Tech</strong> – Automation, precision farming, and sensor-based solutions for agriculture</li>
            <li>🔹 <strong>Industrial Process Optimization</strong> – Innovations for efficiency, automation, and process control in industries</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>General Rules</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>1️⃣ Teams must consist of 2 members from the same college.</li>
            <li>2️⃣ Online registration is mandatory.</li>
            <li>3️⃣ Shortlisted teams will be invited for the finale.</li>
            <li>4️⃣ Final projects must be completed within the given timeframe.</li>
            <li>5️⃣ Final presentations must not exceed 15 minutes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Rewards & Recognition</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>🏆 Winner & Runner-up – Trophy & Certificate</li>
            <li>📜 All Participants – Certificate of Participation</li>
        </ul>

